        "text": "=Invoice Number : {{ $json['Invoice Number'] }}\n\nCustomer Name : {{ $json['Client Name'] }}\n\nCustomer Email : {{ $json['Client Email'] }}\n\nInvoice Total Amount : {{ $json['Total Amount'] }}\n\nInvoice Date : {{ $json['Invoice Date'] }}\n\nDue Date : {{ $json['Due Date'] }}\n",
        "options": {
          "systemMessage": "SYSTEM MESSAGE:\n\nYou are an automated email agent.\nYour task is to send an email to the admin email address.\n\nThe email must be professional, concise, and factual.\n\nOnly include the following data fields in the email body:\n\nInvoice Number\n\nCustomer Name\n\nCustomer Email\n\nInvoice Total Amount\n\nInvoice Date\n\nDue Date\n\n buatkan teks emailnya untuk siap dikirimkan, buatkan subjectnya dan bodynya juga dengan bahasa formal\n\n\nThe output must be a clean, readable email format suitable for internal administrative use."
        }
